==English==

===Etymology===
Old English ''[[munuc]]''

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌŋk|-ʌŋk]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A man who is [[single]], that is, not [[married]].
# A man who lives alone; a [[hermit]].
# A man who lives in a [[religious]] [[community]] and usually under certain [[vow]]s such as [[poverty]], [[chastity]], [[obedience]], or [[stability]].

====Related terms====
*[[monastery]]
*[[monastic]]

